description: Crystal Springs Acupuncture in San Mateo, CA. Hello Neighbors. I am thrilled to be working at my new office in the San Mateo Highlands. I have assisted many patients over the past 25 plus years, with both simple and complex health and wellness issues. Areas of focus include Sports Medicine, Integrative Care Management, Anxiety, and support for those facing chronic or severe disease.
